      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Perform the reorganization and archival of production orders to cover settlement, including quality documentation. Examples of business requirements for archival include: &#10;&#10;Ability to archive data in a manner that is easily retrievable (date, order number, op sequence, qty, etc.) &#10;Ability to maintain archive data for the life of the product/program &#10;Storage and easy retrieval of data should mirror those requirements of inventory control and cycle counting storage and ongoing access requirements. &#10;&#10; &#10;&#10;&#10;INDUSTRY SPECIFIC:  &#10;&#10;&#10;Perform the reorganization and archival of production orders to cover settlement, including quality documentation. Examples of business requirements for archival include:* Ability to archive data in a manner that is easily retrievable* Ability to maintain archive data for the life of the product/program &#10;&#10;"/>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-approvedby" metaValue="[&quot;Shilpa Chandra&quot;]"/>
